                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-77-off449 t18320906-77-cd450"></join>, 1 pair of trousers, value 3s.; 1 waistcoat, value 4s.; 1 pair of shoes, value 1s. 6d.; 1 hat, value 6d., and part of a music-book, value 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18320906-77-victim737" type="victimName">
